cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.HC. 

The paper presents a 3D house simulator designed to train and evaluate autonomous agents, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The simulator also includes support for navigation and manipulation, which could fall under cs.LG (machine learning) or cs.HC (human-computer interaction). Additionally, the paper mentions tasks that combine language and vision, which could fall under cs.CL (computation and language) and cs.CV (computer vision).
